SIMPLE: money-maker
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Money-maker
<hw>Mon"ey-mak`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who coins or prints money; also, a counterfeiter of money.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who accumulates money or wealth; specifically,
one who makes money-getting his governing motive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Money-making</ent>⟦br⟧
